Package ca.uhn.fhir.jpa.subscription

Class SubscriptionActivatingInterceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.fhir.jpa.subscription.SubscriptionActivatingInterceptor
  • @Lazy
public class SubscriptionActivatingInterceptor
extends Object
    Responsible for transitioning subscription resources from REQUESTED to ACTIVE Once activated, the subscription is added to the SubscriptionRegistry.

    Also validates criteria. If invalid, rejects the subscription without persisting the subscription.
